Screen Specifications

Auth (Login/Register)

Purpose: Secure entry and onboarding for researchers.

Layout: Centered terminal-window style modal on a dark grid background.

Key Elements:





Logo Area: Text GphReport v2.0 in Geist Mono, electric cyan.



Input Fields: 40px height, 1px #475569 border, transparent background, placeholder in Geist Mono. Focus state changes border to #00E5FF and adds a 1px cyan glow.



Area Selector (Register): Checkbox grid for Cursos, Projetos, Eventos, Marketing. Checked state fills box with cyan.



Submit Button: Full width, 40px height, solid #00E5FF background, #0B0E14 text, uppercase.

States:





Loading: Submit button text changes to AUTHENTICATING... with blinking underscore.



Error: 1px red border around inputs, laser red text below ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS.

Member Feed

Purpose: Central hub viewing all lab activity.

Layout: Left sidebar (240px), top filter bar (64px), main responsive grid area.

Key Elements:





Sidebar Nav: List of links (Feed, My Reports, Attendance, Dashboard). Active link has a left 2px cyan border and #1E2530 background.



Week Selector: Top right dropdown, monospaced text WEEK_42.



Report Card: 320px width, 200px height. Contains:





Header: Author name, Date (12-OCT-2023).



Badge: Area tag (e.g., [PROJETOS]) in cyan text, 1px cyan border.



Body: 3 lines of truncated report text.



Status: Green dot (Reviewed) or Gray dot (Pending).

States:





Empty: Center text NO_REPORTS_FOUND_FOR_QUERY.



Loading: Skeleton cards with pulsing #1E2530 fills.

Report Editor

Purpose: Creation of weekly hardware progress updates.

Layout: Split pane: Left 70% for rich text and uploads, Right 30% for metadata and publishing controls.

Key Elements:





Editor Canvas: Minimalist markdown-style editor, no toolbar (slash commands).



Media Dropzone: Dashed 1px border (#475569), text DRAG_VIDEO_OR_SCHEMATIC_PDF_HERE.



Area Selector: Radio buttons in the right sidebar.



Deploy Button: Bottom right sticky, cyan background.

Interactions:





Hover Dropzone: Border turns cyan, background shifts to #151A22.



Click Deploy: Button text switches to UPLOADING [||||||....].

Report Viewer

Purpose: Reading and reviewing submitted reports.

Layout: Centered 800px column, floating action bar for managers.

Key Elements:





Title Block: H1 heading, author chip, timestamp.



Media Player: Custom dark-themed HTML5 video player, sharp corners.



PDF Viewer: Inline canvas rendering of the first page with [VIEW_FULL_DOCUMENT] button.



Manager Controls: Fixed bottom bar for users with 'Manager' role. Contains [MARK_REVIEWED] (Neon Green) and [REQUEST_REVISION] (Laser Red).

My Timeline

Purpose: Tracking personal consistency.

Layout: Top summary stats, middle commit-graph, bottom list of personal reports.

Key Elements:





Commit Graph: 52-column grid of 12x12px squares.





Green #39FF14: Submitted on time.



Red #FF2442: Missed week.



Gray #151A22: Future/Empty.



Stat Cards: 3 metrics (Total Reports, Streak, On-time %).

Manager Dashboard

Purpose: Macro-level view of lab operations.

Layout: Top 4 metric cards, middle charts, bottom approval queue table.

Key Elements:





Metric Cards: 240x120px. Large 32px monospaced number, 14px label.



Distribution Chart: Horizontal bar chart showing reports per area. Bars are 8px tall, cyan.



Approval Queue: Table with Author, Area, Wait Time, and [REVIEW] action button.

Attendance Matrix

Purpose: Tracking physical lab presence.

Layout: Full-width dense data table.

Key Elements:





Matrix Table: Columns are meetings (e.g., M-10/12), Rows are members.



Cells: Clickable. Toggles between [X] (Red, absent) and [✓] (Green, present).



Frequency Column: Right-most column showing percentage. Text turns red if < 75%.

Access Control

Purpose: Administering users and roles.

Layout: Dual tables: "Pending Approvals" (top) and "Active Personnel" (bottom).

Key Elements:





Approval Card: Row showing Name, Email, Area. Actions: [APPROVE] (Green), [REJECT] (Red).



Role Select: Native <select> styled with 1px border, options: MEMBER, MANAGER, ADVISOR.



Status Toggle: Switch component (sharp square knob) to disable accounts.





Build Guide

Stack: HTML + Tailwind CSS v3 + React/Next.js

Build Order:





Design System & Layout: Setup tailwind.config.js with exact colors/fonts, build the 1px border wrappers and sidebar layout.



Member Feed: Establishes the core UI patterns (cards, badges, typography hierarchy).



Auth (Login/Register): Form inputs, validation states, and the terminal aesthetic.



Report Editor & Viewer: Complex components (rich text, dropzones, media players).



My Timeline: Custom CSS grid for the commit-graph calendar.



Manager Dash & Attendance: Data-heavy tables and charts.

